## KEY INTERFACES TO IMPLEMENT

**ChannelPlugin Structure:**
- `id`, `meta` - Identification and metadata
- `capabilities` - Feature set (e.g., supports groups, DMs, etc.)
- `config` - Read/write configuration
- `configSchema` - Zod schema + UI hints
- `setupWizard` - Interactive setup
- `messaging` - Inbound message routing
- `outbound` - Send messages
- `security` - Access control
- `pairing` - Unknown sender approval
- `status` - Health monitoring
- `threading` - Reply/thread handling
- `directory` - Peer/group listings
- `groups` - Group policies
- `actions` - Message actions/reactions

