#### `extensions/pulseboard/src/accounts.ts`
Mirrors `extensions/irc/src/accounts.ts`.

- Uses `createAccountListHelpers("pulseboard", { normalizeAccountId })` → exports `listPulseboardAccountIds`, `resolveDefaultPulseboardAccountId`
