> **Implementation note:** During implementation, verify exact export locations by checking `src/plugin-sdk/*.ts` source files. Many utilities exported from `openclaw/plugin-sdk/irc` are also available on generic paths (`openclaw/plugin-sdk/core`, `openclaw/plugin-sdk/status-helpers`, etc.). Use the specific subpath that actually exports each symbol. This barrel exists so the rest of `src/` never imports from `openclaw/plugin-sdk/*` directly.

#### `extensions/pulseboard/src/normalize.ts`
Mirrors `extensions/irc/src/normalize.ts`.

```ts
// isBoardTarget(target): target.startsWith("~")
// normalizePulseboardMessagingTarget(raw):
//   - strips "pulseboard:" prefix
//   - strips "board:" prefix → ensures leading "~"
//   - strips "user:" prefix
//   - returns undefined if target looks invalid
// looksLikePulseboardTargetId(raw): no whitespace, no control chars
